#. <section class="sutta" id="sn51.28"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn51.28:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn51.28:0.2"
msgid "3. Ayoguḷavagga"
msgstr "3. The Iron Ball"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn51.28:0.3"
msgid "28. Dutiyaānandasutta"
msgstr "28. With Ānanda (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.28:1.1"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said to him:"

msgctxt "sn51.28:1.2"
msgid ""
"“katamā nu kho, ānanda, iddhi, katamo iddhipādo, katamā iddhipādabhāvanā, "
"katamā iddhipādabhāvanāgāminī paṭipadā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Ānanda, what is psychic power? What is the basis of psychic power? What is "
"the development of the bases of psychic power? And what is the practice that "
"leads to the development of the bases of psychic power?”"

msgctxt "sn51.28:1.3"
msgid "Bhagavaṃmūlakā no, bhante, dhammā bhagavaṃnettikā … pe …."
msgstr ""
"“Our teachings are rooted in the Buddha. He is our guide and our refuge. …”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.28:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Idhānanda, bhikkhu anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhoti—ekopi hutvā "
"bahudhā hoti … pe … yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vatteti—"
msgstr ""
"“Ānanda, take a mendicant who wields the many kinds of psychic power: "
"multiplying themselves and becoming one again … controlling the body as far "
"as the Brahmā realm."

msgctxt "sn51.28:2.2"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccatānanda, iddhi."
msgstr "This is called psychic power."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.28:3.1"
msgid "Katamo cānanda, iddhipādo?"
msgstr "And what is the basis of psychic power?"

msgctxt "sn51.28:3.2"
msgid "Yo, ānanda, maggo yā paṭipadā iddhilābhāya iddhipaṭilābhāya saṃvattati—"
msgstr "The path and practice that leads to gaining psychic power."

msgctxt "sn51.28:3.3"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccatānanda, iddhipādo."
msgstr "This is called the basis of psychic power."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.28:4.1"
msgid "Katamā cānanda, iddhipādabhāvanā?"
msgstr "And what is the development of the bases of psychic power?"

msgctxt "sn51.28:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idhānanda, bhikkhu chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ "
"bhāveti, "
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion "
"due to enthusiasm … "

msgctxt "sn51.28:4.3"
msgid "vīriyasamādhi … pe …"
msgstr "energy …"

msgctxt "sn51.28:4.4"
msgid "cittasamādhi …"
msgstr "mental development …"

msgctxt "sn51.28:4.5"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti—"
msgstr "inquiry, and active effort."

msgctxt "sn51.28:4.6"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccatānanda, iddhipādabhāvanā."
msgstr "This is called the development of the bases of psychic power."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.28:5.1"
msgid "Katamā cānanda, iddhipādabhāvanāgāminī paṭipadā?"
msgstr ""
"And what is the practice that leads to the development of the bases of "
"psychic power?"

msgctxt "sn51.28:5.2"
msgid "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is:"

msgctxt "sn51.28:5.3"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi—"
msgstr ""
"right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, "
"right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn51.28:5.4"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccatānanda, iddhipādabhāvanāgāminī paṭipadā”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is called the practice that leads to the development of the bases of "
"psychic power.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.28:5.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
